    "Nguyen et al.",
    "19 investigate the Relation Bidirectional Encoder Representations from Transformers (Relation BERT) architecture for detecting and classifying DDIs in biomedical texts.",
    "Three models, R-BERT *, RBioBERT1, and R-BioBERT2, achieve a macro-average F1-score of over 79% and 90.63% and 97% accuracy respectively, promoting the widespread application of automatic DDI extraction.",
