    "20 presents a novel solution using Relation BioBERT (R-BioBERT) and Bidirectional Long Short-Term Memory (BLSTM) to detect and classify Drug-Drug Interactions (DDIs), enhancing prediction accuracy and identifying specific drug interaction types, with higher F-scores."
